VLCcontrols is a cross browser javascript library to add controls to the VLC plugins

Works on IE/Firefox/Chrome/Safari

recent VLC >= 1.0 new security restrictions disable lots of plugin functionnality. now need some serious rewrite so moved to github !

Workings examples : 

simple : http://vlc.revolunet.com/git/example.html
advanced : http://vlc.revolunet.com/git/advanced.html


==== INSTALLATION ====

Put all theses files somewhere on your web server.
Read the doc at : http://www.revolunet.com/labo/code/VLCcontrols